<p>Michelle penned: '#selfie alert.. (#selfiefail) Trying to look cool (Yes, I know I really should know better at 41) Just done a social distance class #fullbodyworkout at <?php echo e('@'); ?>davidlloydbushey.</p>

<p>'<?php echo e('@'); ?>hughhanley is bringing the kids up SO, before having absolutely ZERO intention of getting in the outdoor pool with the kids (I’m sure I can come up with some excuse to stay dry) I do some selfies .. why not.</p>

